org.apache.manifoldcf.core.interfaces

Interface ICacheClass

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BaseDescription.LocalCacheClass

    public interface ICacheClass
    This interface represents an object class. It provides methods that permit the cache manager to learn about the LRU properties of a cached object.
